Ferrovial, Macquire in Puerto Rico Airport Bid, Expansion Says

-- B y   M a n u e l   B a i g o r r i
-- 
2011-08-22T06:24:48Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-22/ferrovial-macquire-in-puerto-rico-airport-bid-expansion-says.html
Ferrovial SA (FER)  and the Australian
investment bank  Macquarie Group Ltd. (MQG)  have set up a group to bid
for the management of Puerto Rico’s Luis Munoz Marin
international airport,  Expansion  reported, without citing
anyone.  The airport reported earnings before interest taxes,
depreciation and amortization of $40 million in 2010, the
newspaper said.  Puerto Rico’s authorities plan to award the concession by
December, Expansion said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Manuel Baigorri in Madrid at 
 mbaigorri@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Angela Cullen at 
 acullen8@bloomberg.net  